# Acceptance tests

Tool used: Vitest

For the status_label functionality, acceptance tests were created based on the "Tu Deporte Aqui" user stories and requirements documentation.

## Running the test:

1) Make sure to install dependencies:
a)Install Vitest  using the following command:

 npm install -D vitest

 2) To run the tests:
Run the following command:
npx vitest --watch

or run the tests once: 
npx vitest

## Run only acceptance test:
Note: By default both property-based tests and acceptance tests will run. 

To run only the acceptance tests, use the following command:
npx vitest run "Tests/Acceptance Test/AcceptanceTest.test.ts"


